{
  "stem": "3874.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they said we all had to go to a special Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, Hitler Youth started-- the Hitler Youth gang started appearing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when you went to school, or when you left school, they would gather outside near the schools, and they would beat the hell out of us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, we'd- some of us would fight back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But on the other hand, I know kids whose parents told them, don't fight back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because if you do fight back, the parents can get arrested.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I mean, there were all kinds of things going on at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, you think that when you're 10 years old, you really don't know much about what's going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You don't necessarily recognize the extent, like an adult would.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But believe me, I knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I knew the dangers that had occurred.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "One of my-- in the Kristallnacht, for instance, my father he'd-- my father had come home that night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He and my uncle-- of my father-- he's his brother, my paternal uncle-- hid in their own factory for that particular night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now we, ourselves, nobody entered our apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But there were a lot of people whose apartments were just trashed-- they would just tear everything-- tear sheets, overturn beds.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They would-- they would break all the dishes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, they just-- I mean, they just would leave a mess of the apartments.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They would beat up the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so that night, one of my uncles was picked up and sent to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he was there for-- for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "At that time, if you could get-- if you could get exit visas, they were still release you from concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
